headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Discounts
content:
All Vehicle Warehouses are 30% off this week. All the better for those looking to get involved in the illicit auto trade and this week’s boost on Vehicle Cargo Sales.

There are also discounts on a range of vehicles including:

- Mammoth Patriot Mil-Spec - 30% off
- Enus Jubilee - 30% off
- Progen PR4 – 20% off
- Weeny Issi Classic – 30% off

And more! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
